{"tid":2431084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[燈王之王]  巴西傳媒報道比利接種科興疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-03T11:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T12:49:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ba53a0f225a4233c5c53f8528c7791b21fb8f664","tid":2431084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"巴西傳媒報道比利接種科興疫苗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=426003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426003&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=3bbb9eee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426003&h=60839c5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=426003</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】球王比利接種新冠疫苗，巴西傳媒報道他接種的是科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n80歲的比利於社交媒體發放一張接種疫苗的相片，他說這天收到疫苗是難忘的一天，並呼籲大家遵守防疫規定，經常洗手並保持社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n巴西的疫情嚴重，更出現變種的新冠病毒，其中巴西球隊哥連泰斯公布錄得19宗確診個案，當中門將卡斯奧據報是再次確診。"},{"pid":"fb35847396cf1d28fef7dd756e40b11ada581a4c","tid":2431084,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08048aa4906788e4ed961095707e10563ff37c4e","tid":2431084,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"打 科興&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n一路好走啦"},{"pid":"4c4ca588ef22dcc826f91620c0c86cb83c36f968","tid":2431084,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"支持球王入藉中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d88e68e95fce34084773301d6424a12d6f70e8f","tid":2431084,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"一路好走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=